16. Full CI/CD pipeline sequence

# Step 1 — build
mvn clean install -DskipTests

# Step 2 — smoke (fast, every commit, < 2 min)
mvn test -pl application-tests -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@smoke" -Denv=qa

# Step 3 — regression (nightly, full suite)
mvn test -pl application-tests \
  -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@regression and not @wip and not @ignore" \
  -Denv=qa \
  -Dschema_validation=true \
  -Dperf_testing=true

# Step 4 — specific API suite (on API change)
mvn test -pl application-tests \
  -Dcucumber.filter.tags="@mosaic or @stp" \
  -Denv=qa
Quick reference — all flags
Flag	What it does	Example
-Denv=	Target environment	-Denv=qa
-Dcucumber.filter.tags=	Which scenarios to run	-Dcucumber.filter.tags="@smoke"
-Dschema_validation=true	Enable JSON schema checks	-Dschema_validation=true
-Dperf_testing=true	Enable SLA response time checks	-Dperf_testing=true
-Dstp.mock=true	Force STP to use WireMock	-Dstp.mock=true
-Dapi.auth.token=	Bearer token for auth	-Dapi.auth.token=abc123
-Dstp.ntlm.username=	NTLM username	-Dstp.ntlm.username=CORP\user
-Dstp.ntlm.password=	NTLM password	-Dstp.ntlm.password=pass
-Dstp.ntlm.domain=	NTLM domain	-Dstp.ntlm.domain=CORP
-DthreadCount=	Parallel thread count	-DthreadCount=4
